Package logic

Class User

java.lang.Object
logic.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
The User class represents a user in the system. This class provides attributes and methods to manage user information such as ID, password, full name, email, phone number, login status, user permission, and associated park name. This class implements Serializable to allow objects of this class to be serialized.
